             sworn. - I saw the prisoner go into the prosecutor's shop; I am sure he is the same man; I did not see him come out again. I picked up the carpet. (The carpeting produced).</p>
               <p>Court. (To Prosecutor.) Q. Is that Kidderminster carpeting? - A. Yes. <rs id="t17980418-35-verdict180" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980418-35-verdict180" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
